"``(float, 0–1)`` **Proboj kromatske boje / obrub.** Horizontalni pomak "
"kromatske boje + zamućenje s blagim desaturiranjem. Daje izgled “duginskog "
"ruba”."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../effects.rst:376
msgid "softness"
msgstr "softness"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../effects.rst:376
msgid ""
"``(float, 0–1)`` **Luma softness.** Small horizontal blur on Y (approx. 0–2 "
"px). Keep low to retain detail when noise is high."
msgstr ""
"``(float, 0–1)`` **Mekoća svjetline.** Malo horizontalno zamućenje na Y "
"(približno 0–2 px). Držite nisko da zadržite detalje kada je šum visok."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../effects.rst:377
msgid "noise"
msgstr "noise"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../effects.rst:377
msgid ""
"``(float, 0–1)`` **Snow, hiss, and dropouts.** Controls grain strength, "
"probability/length of white **streaks**, and a faint line hum."
msgstr ""
"``(float, 0–1)`` **Snijeg, šum i prekidi.** Kontrolira jačinu zrna, "
"vjerojatnost/dužinu bijelih **pruga** i slab šum linije."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../effects.rst:378
msgid "stripe"
msgstr "stripe"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../effects.rst:378
msgid ""
"``(float, 0–1)`` **Tracking stripe.** Lifts the bottom band, adds hiss/noise "
"there, and widens the lifted region as the value increases."
msgstr ""
"``(float, 0–1)`` **Tracking pruga.** Podiže donju traku, dodaje šum/šuštanje "
"tamo i širi podignuto područje kako vrijednost raste."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../effects.rst:379
msgid "static_bands"
msgstr "static_bands"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../effects.rst:379
msgid ""
"``(float, 0–1)`` **Static bursts.** Short bright bands with **row-clumped "
"streaks** (many “shooting stars” across neighboring rows)."
msgstr ""
"``(float, 0–1)`` **Statistički izboji.** Kratke svijetle trake s **skupinama "
"pruga po redovima** (mnoge “padajuće zvijezde” preko susjednih redova)."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../effects.rst:380
msgid "seed_offset"
msgstr "seed_offset"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../effects.rst:380
msgid ""
